{"tid":2233153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指12港人偷渡當日凌晨出動　飛行服務隊稱不評論","createTime":"2020-10-07T02:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T02:44:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"55ddcc2c9cd94a9ac3a7e228de9f3f549686c540","tid":2233153,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"對於有報道指政府飛行服務隊曾在12名港人懷疑偷渡離港當日出動，政府飛行服務隊回覆本台查詢時表示，按一貫做法，飛行任務涉及的飛機調配、航行細節等，不會公開，亦不評論有關報道。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》昨日報道，8月23日即12名港人懷疑潛逃當日，飛行服務隊一輛定翼機凌晨出動，在西貢布袋澳上空盤旋達3小時。另一輛飛行服務隊獵豹直升機曾在12名港人被內地海警拘捕後，飛往涉事地點，並低飛觀察。<br />\n<br />\n有航班追蹤網站顯示，當日飛行服務隊定翼機曾經在西貢一帶上空盤旋，其後飛往東南面海域，期間亦有類以兜圈飛行。至於獵豹直升機，當日曾飛往本港東南面海域，位置和內地當局公布截獲快艇的位置接近。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥昨日被問到政府對12港人坐快艇是否知情時說，不會評論行動細節，強調警方在這案件上絕對沒有任何角色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553411-20201007.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553411-20201007.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=afc2053c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553411-20201007.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=54221679\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553411-20201007.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"451147a8e4e627a08ee9573724c29554e39c78be","tid":2233153,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"身有屎咪唔評論囉，光明正大怕咩講"},{"pid":"b84276cfcf985cec78977e927b040a06489f039e","tid":2233153,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61d2562126d44f8c23cc3dcbcd1ff2bf439f69a3","tid":2233153,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"民望咁高做咩唔評論呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W95UUbJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW95UUbJ.png&h=fa9f3025&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48f5624104b02df9df4fbdefee2f7da0da7837a5","tid":2233153,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"飛狗諗定冇得買airbus問上面買邊款機代替啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae45fb7187129bddb84d76dbcb7ab2c02463078","tid":2233153,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171012/photo/bkn-20171012042507309-1012_00882_001_01p.jpg?20171012052142\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171012%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171012042507309-1012_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20171012052142&h=b3e3f6c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd407077cef5e2dbb44f2be712437e784d1ca59d","tid":2233153,"uid":119767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"正苦有做=不評論<br />\n冇做=否認<br />\n<br />\n有時要decode"},{"pid":"f1b784bd65e6972ac0933d482b6ecd0799401731","tid":2233153,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800013ee88a17cc2785bcc17171a7b78a6e0c91f","tid":2233153,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43b16f30a1828d24e193170e63ad25166d1f833a","tid":2233153,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c770b5fed5caff5ed0a5ff0613625cc1535ded","tid":2233153,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8903aaeb63b023fc7f4da2f7038f5753795de5","tid":2233153,"uid":241291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440e7a97e8220121d91cc71760da8d19ad8fae03","tid":2233153,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"嗯 好嬲"},{"pid":"7106e251dce1beca7f20675fd3e747764d41e588","tid":2233153,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"明白哂<br />\n<br />\n2020年5月25日<br />\n飛行服務隊遲來的表態　<br />\n總監撐國安法：支持特區政府竭力維護國家安全<br />\n<br />\n保安局及多個紀律部隊昨晚到今日凌晨，先後表態支持香港國安法立法，一向較少涉獵政治的政府飛行服務隊今天亦表態，總監胡偉雄撰文，「全力支持建立特區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的決定（草案）」。<br />\n<br />\n胡偉雄指自己支持有關決定，認為政府飛行服務隊作為特區政府一支空中力量，特別是向各紀律部隊提供空中支援，令執法工作更為迅速和有效，「在此政府飛行服務隊會全力支持特區政府履行應有職責，竭力維護國家安全。」<br />\n<br />\n文章又指，過去一年香港暴力不斷升級，巿民生命財產受到威脅及破壞越來越大，「恐怖主義也正在港滋生，危害國家安全的活動更越趨猖獗，令社會充斥暴力，失去安寧」，飛行服務隊已做好準備支持警方果斷執法，亦會全力支持特區政府推行全國人大的草案，建立安全及穩定的社會，確保香港長期繁榮穩定，長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%E9%81%B2%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B-%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%E6%92%90%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AB%AD%E5%8A%9B%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2581%25B2%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B-%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AB%25AD%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=52f42da2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2581%25B2%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B-%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AB%25AD%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%2F&h=f2e24e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%E9%81%B2%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B-%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%E6%92%90%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AB%AD%E5%8A%9B%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/</a>"},{"pid":"3aef7a3db3fb9d8e32b5849791a3eb9aa433512f","tid":2233153,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd407077cef5e2dbb44f2be712437e784d1ca59d","tid":2233153,"uid":119767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"正苦有做=不評論<br />\n冇做=否認<br />\n<br />\n有時要decode"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"有做都可以否認，視乎佢覺得外界有冇證據，當佢肯定外界冇證據時佢就否認"},{"pid":"3b83d10f792d5166b3b69aaa2d611e1509fddf00","tid":2233153,"uid":264326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd407077cef5e2dbb44f2be712437e784d1ca59d","tid":2233153,"uid":119767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"正苦有做=不評論<br />\n冇做=否認<br />\n<br />\n有時要decode"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:32:5